scene.message:
Mariko: I keep hearing screams{nl}
and groans from the room next{nl}
door!{waitkey}{clearbox}It's surely a poltergeist!{nl}
You don't know it? It means a{nl}
"noisy spirit phenomenon"!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: No time limit is{nl}
eerie in its own way. I think{nl}
we'd best hurry on.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: This tower's, like,{nl}
super creepy, y'know? Let's{nl}
get out quick~{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Still, that woman{nl}
Michiko rubs me the wrong{nl}
way! Unpleasant!{waitkey}Truly unpleasant!!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey hey! This tower's{nl}
got no time limit, right?{waitkey}Let's take a rest!{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's keep it breezy! Nice{nl}
and breezy~!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Shouldn't we press on as{nl}
fast as we can? I have such a{nl}
bad feeling{waitkey}I can't shake it.{waitkey}{ret}
